Package Description
gov.ca.water.calgui
Main package for CalLite GUI.
gov.ca.water.calgui.batch
DWR-supplied helper classes for running CalLite in parallel (multiple threads) or on a single thread
gov.ca.water.calgui.bo
In this package we have the Business objects like AuditBO, DataTableModel etc..
gov.ca.water.calgui.bus_delegate
In this package we have the Business Delegate.
gov.ca.water.calgui.bus_delegate.impl  
gov.ca.water.calgui.bus_service
In this package we have the business services like Dynamic control, Monitor, Table etc..
gov.ca.water.calgui.bus_service.impl  
gov.ca.water.calgui.constant
This package has constant values.
gov.ca.water.calgui.presentation
In this package we have the we have the presentation class for the whole application.
gov.ca.water.calgui.presentation.display
This package contains classes used to create sub-displays (charts and tables) that are shown in various presentation layer classes.

In this package we have the technical services like error handling, file system etc.
